data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom and 3 full bathroom house located in Gainesville. This split level plan offers you a large living room with tray ceiling and fireplace. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with stainless steel dishwasher, stove and microwave, plenty of cabinets for storage and a pantry. The main floor living offers you plenty of natural lighting. Owner's suite is a great size and also features the tray ceiling. You will love the soaking tub and separate shower in your en suite. Two secondary bathrooms and a full bath with tub/shower combo finish off your main level. Downstairs you will find a laundry room, another full bath with tub/shower combo and a large finished bonus room that can be used for an office, media room, playroom or converted into a fourth bedroom...so many possibilities. NO HOA allows you so much opportunity for your backyard. The storage building and playset will stay. This home is less than 15 minutes to the trendy, Downtown Gainesville area, 985 and less than 20 minutes to University of North Georgia campus in Oakwood. Don't miss your opportunity to call this one yours! HVAC replaced in July 2023
